^5Help - Friend
~5USAGE: .friend ~5[^5delete~5] ^5user
~5WHERE: ^5user ~5is a user you wish to be a friend of

~5Use this command when you wish to be notified (with a beep) when certain
~5users when log on.  By specifying ^5delete~5 and the name of a user, you
~5will no longer be notified with a beep when that user logs on.

~5Without specifying anything, it will show you your list of friends.

~5EXAMPLES
  ~5.friend
  ~5.friend bob
  ~5.friend del bob

~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help enemy

